data.title: Chronological List of Losing Presidential Candidates of the United States
data.meta_description: This guide provides portraits of each unsuccessful American presidential candidate from the Prints & Photographs Division collections at the Library of Congress.
data.text:
Prints & Photographs: Ask a Librarian

Have a question? Need assistance? Use our online form to ask a librarian for help.

This chronological list contains entries for each presidential hopeful and the year in which they ran.
